title: I AM TANK

embed.description: I AM TANK, A poem by Iridium Devil Original post; http://forums.na.leagueoflegends.com/board/showthread.php?p=19952325 If you're interested in getting involved in a project, contact me on Twitter, OR, join this Discord group for creative people. body: I've spent a while on this video, and it's probably my best one to date. Enjoy!
